    "advancement": [],
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"495\" data-end=\"541\">Voice of Calm (Bonus Action; 1/Short Rest)</strong><br data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"544\" />Your presence tempers fury and steadies the spirit.</p><p data-start=\"597\" data-end=\"727\"><strong data-start=\"597\" data-end=\"614\">Bonus Action:</strong> Choose <strong data-start=\"622\" data-end=\"653\">one creature within 30 feet</strong> that can see or hear you. Until the <strong data-start=\"690\" data-end=\"726\">end of that creature’s next turn</strong>:</p><ul data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"958\"><li data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"822\"><p data-start=\"730\" data-end=\"822\">The creature has <strong data-start=\"747\" data-end=\"777\">advantage on saving throws</strong> against being <strong data-start=\"792\" data-end=\"806\">frightened</strong> or <strong data-start=\"810\" data-end=\"821\">charmed</strong>.</p></li><li data-start=\"823\" data-end=\"958\"><p data-start=\"825\" data-end=\"958\">If the creature is <strong data-start=\"844\" data-end=\"854\">raging</strong> (or under a similar rage-like effect), it has <strong data-start=\"901\" data-end=\"957\">advantage on its next Frenzy / loss-of-control check</strong>.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"960\" data-end=\"1014\"><strong data-start=\"960\" data-end=\"1014\">Auspice Ribbon (Choose One at Subclass Selection):</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1015\" data-end=\"1554\"><li data-start=\"1015\" data-end=\"1117\"><p data-start=\"1017\" data-end=\"1117\"><strong data-start=\"1017\" data-end=\"1030\">Ragabash:</strong> The target may immediately move up to 10 feet without provoking opportunity attacks.</p></li><li data-start=\"1118\" data-end=\"1231\"><p data-start=\"1120\" data-end=\"1231\"><strong data-start=\"1120\" data-end=\"1132\">Theurge:</strong> The target also gains advantage on its next saving throw against a spell or supernatural effect.</p></li><li data-start=\"1232\" data-end=\"1353\"><p data-start=\"1234\" data-end=\"1353\"><strong data-start=\"1234\" data-end=\"1247\">Philodox:</strong> If the target fails a saving throw during the duration, it may reroll the save and take the new result.</p></li><li data-start=\"1354\" data-end=\"1449\"><p data-start=\"1356\" data-end=\"1449\"><strong data-start=\"1356\" data-end=\"1369\">Galliard:</strong> One additional creature within 10 feet of the target gains the base benefits.</p></li><li data-start=\"1450\" data-end=\"1554\"><p data-start=\"1452\" data-end=\"1554\"><strong data-start=\"1452\" data-end=\"1463\">Ahroun:</strong> If the target makes an attack during the duration, it gains a +2 bonus to the damage roll.</p></li></ul>",
